Better People, Smarter Fit

BCS Placement is an agency specializing in the international logistics and supply chain industries representing employers, recruits and new entrants. We strive to make mutually successful placements and guarantee our performance.






Listening

Companies come in all sizes, and individuals fit best in certain places. We work to match the skills and environment for employers and individuals.





Networking

We have cultivated relationships with companies, trade associations and individuals around the United States. By networking in local markets around the country, we have earned a reputation as logistics industry placement leader.





Guaranteeing

There is a lot of time and effort that goes into creating a successful employer / employee partnership. If a client is not satisfied, we will either reimburse for temporary positions or find a replacement for permanent positions.










Are You ...




An Employer


Making a Career Change


A Recruit








Placing Candidates For





Air Freight

Import or export, airline or forwarder, warehouse or ramp, many candidates with current TSA STA’s.





Sea Freight

Freight forwarders, VOCCs and NVOCCs, booking, documentation, customer service, rate management.





Trucking

Over-the-road and local drivers, CDL with hazmat endorsements, specialized equipment and teams.






Warehousing

Operations, management, pick-and-pack, outbound and reverse logistics.





Customs

Import operations, licensed Customs brokers, experienced in many parts of the tariff and with Participating Government Agencies (PGA’s).





Brokerage

Carrier negotiation, load scheduling, booking, tracking and in-transit monitoring with knowledge of carriers and networked representatives.








